---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — LUTkyLab"
  description="Privacy policy for LUTkyLab (lutkylab.com). How we handle data, cookies, and your rights under GDPR and Malaysia's PDPA."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[720px] px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] mb-2 text-sm">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        LUTkyLab (lutkylab.com) is a content site for DJI creators. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data.
      </p>

      <h2>Data I collect</h2>
      <h3>Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        I use Google Analytics (or a privacy-respecting alternative) to understand how readers find and use this site. This includes page views, traffic sources, and device types. IP addresses are anonymized. No personally identifiable information is collected through analytics.
      </p>

      <h3>Advertising (Google AdSense)</h3>
      <p>
        This site displays advertisements provided by Google AdSense. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this or other websites. You can opt out of personalized ads via <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Google's Ad Settings</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>Affiliate links</h3>
      <p>
        When you click an Amazon affiliate link, Amazon may set cookies to track purchases. See <a href="https://www.amazon.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h3>Contact form / email</h3>
      <p>
        If you contact me via email, I store your email address and message only to respond to your inquiry. I do not share this information with third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This site uses cookies for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your dark/light mode preference (stored locally in your browser)</li>
        <li>Google Analytics tracking</li>
        <li>Google AdSense advertising</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You can clear cookies at any time via your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>
        If you are based in the European Union, you have rights under GDPR including: the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data; the right to object to processing; and the right to data portability. To exercise these rights, contact me at hello@lutkylab.com.
      </p>

      <h2>Malaysia PDPA</h2>
      <p>
        Under Malaysia's Personal Data Protection Act 2010 (PDPA), I process personal data only for legitimate purposes related to operating this website. I do not sell or rent personal data to third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — <a href="https://www.amazon.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Privacy Notice</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        I may update this policy periodically. Changes will be noted with an updated date at the top of this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy: <a href="/contact">contact page</a> or hello@lutkylab.com.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
